==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unread
<hw>Un*read"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not read
or perused; <as>as, an <ex>unread</ex> book</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Hooker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not versed in literature; illiterate.</def>
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unreadiness</ent>⟦br⟧
